                        {
                            "id": "616ab59",
                            "settings": {
                                "editor": "<p>Discuss the impact of blockchain on supply chain transparency, traceability, and efficiency, reducing fraud and enhancing trust. Investigate how artificial intelligence and blockchain technology can complement each other, driving innovation in various industries.</p>",
                                "text_color": "#FFFFFF"
                            },
                            "widgetType": "text-editor",
                            "elType": "widget"
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "c1da9d4",
                            "settings": {
                                "title": "Blockchain and Sustainable Development",
                                "title_color": "#FFFFFF"
                            },
                            "widgetType": "heading",
                            "elType": "widget"
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "a9ed407",
                            "settings": {
                                "editor": "<p>Explore how blockchain technology can contribute to sustainable development goals, environmental conservation, and responsible business practices. Blockchain in Healthcare: Investigate the applications of blockchain in healthcare, such as patient data management, drug traceability, and securing health records.</p>",
                                "text_color": "#FFFFFF"
                            },
                            "widgetType": "text-editor",
                            "elType": "widget"
                        },
