                        {
                            "id": "6624d84",
                            "settings": {
                                "editor": "<p>We continued our partnership with SoFi, allowing their members to access the world of crypto with exciting new features and benefits. Our CEO, Peter Smith, shared his thoughts on the migration process for these users, and looks forward at how this changes Blockchain.com\u2019s Community.</p><p>This information is provided for informational purposes only and is not intended to substitute for obtaining accounting, tax or financial advice from a professional advisor.</p><p>The purchase of crypto entails a risk. The value of crypto can fluctuate and capital involved in a crypto transaction is subject to market volatility and loss.</p><p>Digital currencies are not bank deposits, are not legal tender, and are not backed by the government. Blockchain.com\u2019s products and services are not subject to any governmental or government-backed deposit protection schemes. Legislative and regulatory changes or actions in any jurisdiction in which Blockchain.com\u2019s customers are located may adversely affect the use, transfer, exchange, and value of digital currencies.</p><p>Zeta is available to buy, sell, swap, trade, and hold in your Blockchain.com Account now. Find out all the information you need to know about the latest token added in this article.</p><p>You can also start earning daily bonuses with Zeta simply:</p><p>1. Buy or swap into Zeta within your Account<br />Unlock ZetaChain rewards. Buy or swap Zeta within your Blockchain.com account, seamlessly. Start now.</p><p>2. Unlock daily a bonus, right into your Account<br />Your Zeta holdings pay a bonus on a daily basis, right into your Blockchain.com Account. Proportional to your share of the total Zeta within the Blockchain.com platform.</p><p>Any reward rate referenced herein is not guaranteed and is subject to change in accordance with Passive Rewards terms of the Blockchain.com User Agreement. Digital currencies and the Passive Rewards Account in particular are not bank deposits, are not legal tender, and are not backed by the government. Blockchain.com\u2019s products and services are not subject to any governmental or government-backed deposit protection schemes. Legislative and regulatory changes or actions in any jurisdiction in which Blockchain.com\u2019s customers are located may adversely affect the use, transfer, exchange, and value of digital currencies.</p>",
                                "text_color": "#FFFFFF"
                            },
                            "widgetType": "text-editor",
                            "elType": "widget"
                        }
                    ],
                    "elType": "container",
                    "isInner": true
                }
